Class AlgorithmSelector.FileAutoTaggerPair

java.lang.Object
  gui.AlgorithmSelector.FileAutoTaggerPair
Enclosing class:
AlgorithmSelector
private class AlgorithmSelector.FileAutoTaggerPair
extends java.lang.Object

This inner class is used to simplify the saving of two object as data for each table item, since we want to save a file name and also an autotagger object if one is created. This is so that we don't have to create an AutoTagger object again if it already was created.

Author:
Or Shwartz
